  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The result of a stupid struggle has made a person ignored by the people as President - Vimal",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The president has resigned after ordering never to use firearms against protesters.",
        "The person who is going to react to the protesters has become the President. Vimal Weerawansa, president of the National Freedom Front, said that the result of the stupid struggle has made Ranil Wickramasinghe, who was ignored by the people, the president.",
        "He mentioned the above while attending a press conference held on Thursday 21st at the office of the National Freedom Front in Colombo.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, who won the election with the support of 69 lakh people, resigned due to the people's protest, and the leader of the United National Party, Ranil Wickremesinghe, who was ignored by the people and lost the election, has been elected as the president with the support of Podujana Peramuna.",
        "I have mentioned many times in the Parliament that to solve the basic problem facing the country, a solution should be found in a selfless way, if the current crisis is observed with selfish motives, other parties will get the benefit of it.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe was sworn in as the Prime Minister as a result of the protest on May 09, and he was sworn in as the Acting President as a result of the July 09 protest.",
        "We did not urge ex-President Gotabaya Rajapaksa to step down considering the critical nature of his resignation. The protesters lacked the experience to understand political operations.",
        "The president who ordered the protesters not to use guns when they besieged the presidential palace has resigned, the person who reacts to the protesters has been sworn in as the president. Ranil Wickremesinghe has become the president because of the stupid protest.",
        "Most of the members of parliament have chosen Ranil Wickremesinghe as the president considering their personal safety. The people of the country will now understand the improper activities of President Ranil Wickremesinghe by mentioning it as democracy."
      ],
